                    "type": "p",
                    "text": [
                        "This block has a solid colour background and it's block margins attribute is set to ",
                        "<q>top</q>. The content of this block should have a gap between it's neighbouring block ",
                        "above and be flush with the block below."
                    ]
                }
            ]
        }
    },

